4.) assume that you are a home computer user and amateur photographer with 
almost 20GB of digital photographs stored on your hard disk. you are running 
short of disk space and you want archive current and future photographs on to 
removable optical disks. investigate capacity and cost per various recordable 
and rewritable CD and DVD media. which media type offers the lowest cost? which 
should you choose and why?
